Installing Groovy On Windows Machine:

1. Download Groovy Binary and keppt in C:
2. Unzip it
3. Open the Groovy Folder and Navigate to C:\groovy-2.4.13\bin Folder
4. Copy the Path
5. Add GROOVY_HOME Environment System variable
	  GROOVY_HOME:C:\groovy-2.4.13
6. Add C:\groovy-2.4.13\bin to Path Variable

7. Then test installation:

   C:\Users\Raj>groovy -version
   Groovy Version: 2.4.13 JVM: 1.8.0_151 Vendor: Oracle Corporation OS: Windows 10

   C:\Users\Rajgroovyc -version
   Groovy compiler version 2.4.13
   Copyright 2003-2017 The Apache Software Foundation. http://groovy-lang.org/
	  
